snippet.title: Evil Seal - New Official Trailer
snippet.description:
https://tinyurl.com/3ta6fmcf
Evil Seal is an action horror videogame inspired by the Apocalypse of St. John.
The story begins when the first of the Seven Seals is broken and the first of the Four Knights begin to spread confusion and destruction on Earth.
